description: This Chainlink VRF top 15% score Yulenka purrs with a rating of 65, and a multiplier of 2x. It has a total score of 130, and confers the same amount of votes in the EtherCats DAO. The card game properties are 8 for North, Stringalong for East, 1 for South, and Nine Lives for West. Yulenka has the personality suit of yenta. A rendering of the card can be found at https://cards.ethercats.eth.link/80652-87194-3.html. Each Founders Series cat is part of NFT history. These fine felines represent the first verifiably random NFTs minted with Chainlink VRF.
name: Yulenka [130 Votes, Top 15% Score]
